Name: Drumpf: Rise Up, Libertonia!
About the game: Drumpf: Rise Up, Libertonia! is an erotic 2D RPG set in the fictional land of Amerika. In Drumpf: Rise Up, Libertonia!, you take the mantle of Drumpf; once God-Emperor of the super-continent of Amerika, yet now downtrodden and deposed by his former compatriots. Once revered as a bastion of freedom and democracy, the super-continent of Amerika has been corrupted by the Usurpers; dictators who helped overthrow the rightful rulers of the world.
